. || 3rd || 48:38 || [[2017\u201318 SHL season#(2) Djurg\u00e5rdens IF vs. (9) Link\u00f6pings HC|SHL Quarterfinals]] || '''[[Link\u00f6pings HC]]''' || 3\u20132 || [[Djurg\u00e5rdens IF Hockey|Djurg\u00e5rdens IF]] || March 20, 2018 || [[Chad Billins]]\n|}\n\n===KHL===\nThis is a list of [[Kontinental Hockey League]] games that went to at least the third overtime.\n\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n|-\n! style=\"background:#ddf;\" colspan=\"2\"| Overtime\n! style=\"background:#ddf;\"| Overtime length<br/>(min:sec)\n! style=\"background:#ddf;\"| Home Team\n! style=\"background:#ddf;\"| Score\n! style=\"background:#ddf;\"| Away Team\n! style=\"background:#ddf;\"| Date\n! style=\"background:#ddf;\"| Scorer\n! style=\"background:#ddf;\"| Ref\n|-\n|1. || 5th || 82:09 || [[HC CSKA Moscow]] || 1\u20132 || [[Jokerit]] || March 22, 2018 || [[Mika Niemi]] ||\n|-\n|2. || 4th || 66:14 || [[HC Lev Praha|Lev Praha]] || 3\u20134 || [[HC Donbass]] || March 21, 2014 || [[Andrei Konev]] ||<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://en.khl.ru/report/245/?idgame=41390 |title=Archived copy |access-date=March 22, 2014 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140322051834/http://en.khl.ru/report/245/?idgame=41390 |archive-date=March 22, 2014 |url-status=dead |df=mdy-all }}</ref>\n|-\n|3.||3rd || 58:48 || [[Severstal Cherepovets]] || 3\u20132 || [[Lokomotiv Yaroslavl]] || February 25, 2013 || [[Denis Kazionov]] ||<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://en.khl.ru/report/223/?idgame=37496 |title=Archived copy |access-date=March 22, 2014 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140322141157/http://en.khl.ru/report/223/?idgame=37496 |archive-date=March 22, 2014 |url-status=dead |df=mdy-all }}</ref>\n|-\n|4.|| 3rd || 56:35 || [[Admiral Vladivostok]] || 2\u20133 || [[Metallurg Magnitogorsk]] || March 12, 2014 || [[Danis Zaripov]] ||<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://en.khl.ru/report/245/?idgame=41265 |title=Archived copy |access-date=March 22, 2014 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140316204856/http://en.khl.ru/report/245/?